{"metadata": {"page_hash": "2645e07c7d8a1ef8660868235fa024fa5467f97549f90e96803a4f288140ec64", "original_filename": "1503.05621.pdf", "page_no": 19, "num_pages": 33, "original_width": 612, "original_height": 792, "coco_width": 1025, "coco_height": 1025, "collection": "arxiv_doublespaced", "doc_category": "scientific_articles"}, "form": [{"id_box": 26372, "box": [90.44117647058823, 74.62062121212136, 360.1458423202614, 13.739490845959494], "id_box_line": 0, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 74.62062121212136, 360.1458423202614, 13.739490845959494], "text": "Linear Gaussian State Space Models", "category": "Section-header", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/WOCEHX+CMBX12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 1, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1196903594771, 13.739490845959608], "text": "We construct two linear Gaussian state space models (Durbin and Koopman, 2012) each consisting", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 2, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 146.4962225378788, 844.1179485294117, 13.739490845959722], "text": "of 100 latent states and observations. State transitions are governed by a first order AR process, and", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 3, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 177.4377888257577, 844.1097753267975, 13.739490845959494], "text": "we seek inferences about the transition process, and the system and observation noise. We consider", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 4, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 208.3793551136364, 844.1095743464052, 13.739490845959608], "text": "two equivalent parameterizations of the state transition process. First, in terms of the intercept and", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 5, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 239.31957544191914, 844.1100767973858, 13.739490845959608], "text": "mean of the AR process, which have largely uncorrelated posteriors (independent parameterization),", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 6, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 270.26114172979806, 844.122035130719, 13.739490845959608], "text": "and second, in terms of the intercept and autocorrelation, which are known to be highly correlated", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 7, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 301.20270801767685, 844.1178480392157, 13.739490845959494], "text": "(correlated parameterization). For the correlated parameterization, we consider an informed MCMC", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 8, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 332.14427430555554, 844.1139624183006, 13.739490845959608], "text": "algorithm, which blocks the intercept and autocorrelation parameters. We deliberately include this", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 9, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 363.08584059343434, 844.1259207516341, 13.739413194444523], "text": "inferior parameterization, to assess MCMC performance in the case of known strong posterior", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 10, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 394.02609974747475, 844.1258202614379, 13.739426136363704], "text": "correlation. In practice, an analyst may not know which model parameterization(s) will produce", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26373, "box": [90.44117647058823, 115.55465625, 844.1259207516341, 323.1523970959596], "id_box_line": 11, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 424.967627209596, 294.9469154411765, 13.73942613636359], "text": "uncorrelated posterior dimensions.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 13, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 518.4937004419193, 844.1177475490197, 13.73941319444441], "text": "We consider a spatially dependent hierarchical model. The data consist of 148 measurements of", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 14, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 549.4352279040404, 844.121834150327, 13.739413194444467], "text": "scallop abundance at various locations off the New York and New Jersey coastline, and was collected", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 15, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 580.3767424242425, 844.1138619281046, 13.73942613636359], "text": "by the Northeast Fisheries Science Center of the National Marine Fisheries Service in 1993. The", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 16, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 611.3170145202021, 260.71156372549024, 13.739413194444467], "text": "data set is publicly available at", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 17, "box_line": [356.31311274509807, 612.6012152777778, 535.7795420751634, 12.888443181818218], "text": "http://www.biostat.umn.edu/~brad/data/myscallops.txt", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/BQPVAM+CMTT12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 18, "box_line": [892.0950163398693, 611.3170145202021, 42.46084272875828, 13.739413194444467], "text": ", and", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 19, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 642.2585419823232, 844.1279640522876, 13.739413194444523], "text": "is analyzed in Banerjee, Carlin, and Gelfand (2003), pages 44-65. Following Banerjee, Carlin, and", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 20, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 673.2000694444445, 844.1238774509804, 13.73941319444441], "text": "Gelfand (2003), we model the mean log-abundance as multivariate normal with covariance that de-", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 21, "box_line": [90.44117647058823, 704.1416098484849, 634.0125441176469, 13.73941319444441], "text": "cays exponentially as a function of distance. The covariance is given by cov(", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 22, "box_line": [724.4438558006536, 704.1416098484849, 38.95793872549018, 13.73941319444441], "text": "g$_{i}$, g$_{j}$", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/DJAHZF+CMMI12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 23, "box_line": [765.0050318627451, 704.1416098484849, 28.440685049019635, 13.73941319444441], "text": ") =", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 24, "box_line": [799.0025567810458, 704.1416098484849, 11.14280514705888, 13.73941319444441], "text": "\u03c3", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/DJAHZF+CMMI12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 25, "box_line": [810.8637495915033, 704.1416098484849, 48.842439133987, 13.73941319444441], "text": "$^{2}$exp(", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/AYMNBA+CMR8", "size": 7.970099925994873}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 26, "box_line": [859.7036262254902, 703.275161300505, 15.573920343137274, 14.605861742424224], "text": "\u2212", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/XENQGP+CMSY10", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 27, "box_line": [875.2779485294117, 704.1416098484849, 46.20981372549022, 13.73941319444441], "text": "d$_{i,j}$/\u03c1", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/DJAHZF+CMMI12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 28, "box_line": [921.4883651960783, 704.1416098484849, 13.071078022875895, 13.73941319444441], "text": "),", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 29, "box_line": [90.4411245506536, 735.0831631944445, 455.6275752042484, 13.73941319444441], "text": "where the observations are modeled as Poisson counts", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 30, "box_line": [551.5839366830065, 735.0831631944445, 14.386477941176508, 13.73941319444441], "text": "y$_{i}$", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/DJAHZF+CMMI12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 31, "box_line": [572.3669673202614, 734.2167017045455, 15.573920343137274, 14.605874684343405], "text": "\u223c", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/XENQGP+CMSY10", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 32, "box_line": [593.5034052287582, 735.0831631944445, 109.41377573529417, 13.73941319444441], "text": "Poisson(exp(", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 33, "box_line": [702.9087565359476, 735.0831631944445, 14.217302696078605, 13.73941319444441], "text": "g$_{i}$", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/DJAHZF+CMMI12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 34, "box_line": [717.9605130718954, 735.0831631944445, 58.01067892156857, 13.73941319444441], "text": ")), and", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 35, "box_line": [781.4820408496732, 735.0831631944445, 24.691312091503164, 13.73941319444441], "text": "d$_{i,j}$", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/DJAHZF+CMMI12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 36, "box_line": [813.2955453431373, 735.0831631944445, 121.26337867647055, 13.73941319444441], "text": "is the distance", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 37, "box_line": [90.4411245506536, 766.0247035984848, 181.43645755718958, 13.739413194444467], "text": "between observations", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/JJXYBJ+CMR12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 38, "box_line": [278.8334632352941, 766.0247035984848, 14.386477941176452, 13.739413194444467], "text": "y$_{i}$", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/DJAHZF+CMMI12", "size": 11.9552001953125}}, {"id_box": 26374, "box": [90.44107430555556, 518.4937004419193, 844.1280662173203, 292.2106625631312], "id_box_line": 39, "box_line": [301.00662500000